<%# Auto-submit fires on every toggle change. The response targets the
    page-level aria-live region (#notifications-live) so screen reader users
    get an explicit "Preferences saved" announcement after each change —
    without an announcement, the auto-submit is silent for SR users. %>
<%= turbo_stream.update "notifications-live" do %><%= t("notifications.preferences.update.saved_announcement") %><% end %>
